ds4.c (dwarfstar) - the DeepSeek-V4-Flash C reference engine

The QAT simulation round-trips (fp8/fp4/Hadamard chains), compressor QAT
sites, and sink-attention semantics in gmlx/deepseek_v4_model.py are
reimplemented from ds4.c's reference behavior (functions cited in comments);
numeric parity against ds4.c gates the port. ds4.c is distributed under the
